desc: MyDesignerrPlugg is a local showcase warehouse base in Atlanta,Ga . We’ve been in business for years with our private clients, now it’s time to broadcast our services to world. We are known for our discounted designer bags and clothing & local designers to showcase and sell custom exclusive pieces through our brand.
